'''天主教拉多姆教區'''（{{lang-la|Dioecesis Radomensis}}）是[[波蘭|波蘭]]一個[[羅馬天主教|羅馬天主教]][[教區|教區]]。教區位於波蘭東南部，屬[[天主教琴斯托霍瓦總教區|琴斯托霍瓦總教區]]。1992年3月25日自'''桑多米日-拉多姆教區'''分出<ref>{{cite journal|journal=[[宗座公報|宗座公報]]|publisher=梵蒂岡出版社|volume=84|title=Nova Polonicarum circumscriptionum ecclesiasticarum compositio.|page=1099|url=http://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS%2084%20%5B1992%5D%20-%20ocr.pdf|access-date=2011-04-01|archive-date=2020-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200713051903/http://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS%2084%20%5B1992%5D%20-%20ocr.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2011年，在當地920,000人口中，有教友912,900人，佔轄區總人口99.2%、299個堂區、776名司鐸、99名修士、519名修女。

現任主教為{{link-en|亨利·托馬西克|Henryk Tomasik|亨利·瑪利亞諾·托馬西克}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=RINUNCE E NOMINE, 16.10.2009 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2009/10/16/0641/01503.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2019-10-07 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191007110656/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2009/10/16/0641/01503.html |archivedate=2019-10-07 |language=it |date=2009-10-16 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，輔理主教為{{link-pl|伯多祿·圖任斯基|Piotr Turzyński}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=Rinunce e nomine, 17.01.2015 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2015/01/17/0044/00091.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2019-10-07 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191007111528/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2015/01/17/0044/00091.html |archivedate=2019-10-07 |language=it |date=2015-01-17 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，榮休輔理主教為{{link-pl|亞當·奧齊梅克|Adam Odzimek}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=Rinunce e nomine, 07.10.2019 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2019/10/07/0783/01594.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2019-10-07 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191007104454/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2019/10/07/0783/01594.html |archivedate=2019-10-07 |language=it |date=2019-10-07 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

